description:
On October 31st 2014, the world is driven to chaos as the dreded Zombie Apocalypse happens for real. It's up to nine friends to come together and try to make it out alive, or die trying. However, all goes down the shit hole when the triplets(Sonic, Manic, and Sonia) mother is attacked by a zombie and winds up getting scratched, which she claims was not caused by the zombie. This winds up causing friction among the already worn out and emotionally crushed team as some defend her, while others want to get rid of her, no matter the cost.

Tamers12345 directs "Sonic Underground: Zombie Apocalypse" which stars Sonic The Hedgehog, Manic The Hedgehog, Sonia The Hedgehog, Knuckles The Echidna, Mindy Latour, Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin, Queen Aleena, Uncle Chuck, and Mindy Latour's father.

Like my videos? Then how about supporting my patreon? https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
